{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","role":"symbol","platforms":[{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"macOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"title":"OUDSSwitchItem","roleHeading":"Structure"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and optional texts and a custom switch trait.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ Localizable from bundle can also be used","    OUDSSwitchItem(LocalizedStringKey(\"notifications_setting\"), bundle: Bundle.module, isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and a description text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, description: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, description: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additional label, a description text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   description: \"The Beatles\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, a description text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   description: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   isError: true,","                   errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, flipLeadingIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-switch"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2},{"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeCompact"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.5.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.14.0"}]}],"name":"Since"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:isOn:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\